    "James W. Knox": "In his book, when he came to the part about the fall of the Khazar empire, he noted that \u201cwhere the historians\u2019 resources give out, legend and folklore provide useful hints.\u201d Should you even for a moment be tempted to believe the Khazar theory, please read that quote again."
